? ? ??? 2002, 

- Some improvements in typing speed
- Added possibility to include xslt-stylesheets in the transform xslts.
- Made a lot of changes for allowing mixed case tagnames.
- Added save method to http transport driver

16 Sep 2002, Version 0.20020916
- Added using of attribute method for schema files.
- Added simple example to insert images.
- Added possibility to take options from url-query with attribute
    isParam="true" like in the files section.
- Added possibility to take the path to config.xml from url-query
- Element with id="bxe_area" is replaced on startup, not just body element
